/**
 * Fitting sample images for the cookbook demo casts, one per image-bearing
 * recipe. Generated with FAL flux-schnell (`nodetool generate`), resized and
 * JPEG-compressed, then inlined as base64 data URIs so each cast stays
 * backend-free and self-contained — the same pattern as `exampleImage.ts`,
 * but distinct per recipe so no two demos share the same placeholder.
 */

